{"type": "article", "id": 19404, "title": "人生啊，时间并不只是在年末才觉得过得特别快的！", "description": "年末岁初，适合感慨：尼玛。", "date": "2015-12-20T08:15:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 18, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 137, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141430nlPxYuQyUIGKSBzR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>1. 离 2016 还有不到两周。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141417n7rsB3vMxKIVJzqR.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.778\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>2. 房租<strong>又该交了</strong>。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614141859KgtoDwBiy0SVTY.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.61721068\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>3. <strong>刘海<strong>又该剪了</strong></strong>。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061414196czCJAfqISaB0vPX.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>4. 同学结婚请柬</strong><span><strong>/</strong></span><strong>朋友圈晒娃。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141419vTxNr97jLbzu5XB1.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>5. 亲戚家的婴儿长成熊孩子。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061414209EpirFyzSfxUeRa0.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.484\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>6. 亲戚再不问期末考试问单身。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141420EKpfQWbs7NJU93Ci.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.752\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>7.“叔叔</strong><span><strong>/</strong></span><strong>阿姨好。”——早就习惯了。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061414212KDWgY8cLPAiO03y.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>8. 有些人更美。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141422Ei58fZoMwcShGmrF.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.26857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>9. 有些人长残了。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145911wnsVlieIMUt2EC96.gif\" width=\"320\" height=\"163\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.509375\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b>10. 有些人一会美一会残。</b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141422WJsbGYTvuO7FfAXi.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.426\" data-format=\"gif\"></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b>11. 有些人更出名。</b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141423kFqMhSPsKvDYcaoz.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.68535826\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong>12. 有些人坚持不变。</strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145912h7Bj2XwlmrZgeRHJ.jpg\" width=\"371\" height=\"220\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.59299191\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>13.以前是星仔，现在是星爷。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141423w3QJIh6EbfrU5Cp4.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>14. 以前是水手月亮，现在是巴拉拉小魔仙。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061414240B6QEVfZqku3GSz4.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.734\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>15.以前是红白机，现在是 IPAD。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141424FyIgs0xZlQJGP9Xt.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.8230384\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>16. 周杰伦生了女儿。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614142561vBcCy0OrGUQRPZ.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.88115942\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>17.《还珠格格》 </strong><span><strong>17 </strong></span><strong>周年。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061414250A3UaDo4h9VNEye5.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.64528302\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>18. 《康熙来了》要完结。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141426QhWR0nuxJiagcKGM.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>19.说点近的，小 </strong><span><strong>S </strong></span><strong>和黄子佼的世纪和解，发生在今年</strong><span><strong> 1 </strong></span><strong>月。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141426uMGbXP7d52HZykJt.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.76388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>20. 麦迪远去，科比退役。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141427JVpNsCztX4fPF6dm.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>21.很久以前这街不是长这样。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141427IqcQY7vG1WdPzxgX.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>22.很久以前有家好吃的店。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141427i48MUB9SvDA53EnV.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>23.很久以前有某个人。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141428tUAdOFkQYKlgIco7.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.31875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong>24. 十年前，不是 1995 年，是 2005 年。</strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong> </strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141429tcBvnuMpCo6PONX9.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.73\" data-format=\"gif\"> </strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><span></span>25.今年回家的火车票，抢到了吗？</strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061414303Md2kpYwetZ1qXB7.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong> <em>好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。</em></strong> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}